" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2531438\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 26, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104quu1665702914307.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quu1665702914307.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quu1665702914307.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"quu1665702914307\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Date and Time Data Types\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702914307__section_w4434ab1b5b1_w4435ab1b5_w4436ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702914307__section_bkv_j1f_ncc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d733542e59\">Date and Time Data Types</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702914307__p_d44756e1_d44757e1_d44758e1\">If a Date or Time field uses an E packing code,\n            Uniface automatically adds a NULL date or time to the date to be stored.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702914307__section_ttz_l1f_ncc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d733542e68\">Datetime Data Type</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702914307__p_d44762e1_d44763e1_d44764e1\">For a Datetime field, Uniface provides defaults in the\n            case of partially filled fields:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"quu1665702914307__ul_twn_n1f_ncc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quu1665702914307__li_d22223e1_d22224e1_d22225e1\">If both the date and time have been omitted, the\n               value is assumed to be NULL. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quu1665702914307__li_d22226e1_d22227e1_d22228e1\">If the date has been omitted but a time is\n               specified, the day, month and year default to the current day, the current month and\n               the current year, respectively. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"quu1665702914307__li_d22229e1_d22230e1_d22231e1\">If an incomplete date is specified, a missing day\n               defaults to 1, a missing month defaults to the current month, and a missing year\n               defaults to the current year. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"quu1665702914307__section_bl2_41f_ncc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d733542e89\">Linear Date and Time Data Types</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702914307__p_d44768e1_d44769e1_d44770e1\">The range of values that a Linear Date field can have\n            is from 0 (days) through 10,000 years (that is, 3,652,425 days). Only a whole number of\n            days is allowed; that is, you cannot specify hours, minutes and ticks.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702914307__p_d44771e1_d44772e1_d44773e1\">The range of values that Linear Time may have is 0 to\n            24 hours. If more specific time information is required, use the Linear Datetime or\n            Linear Date data type format.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quu1665702914307__p_d44774e1_d44775e1_d44776e1\">The range of values that a Linear Datetime field can\n            have is from 0 days up to 10,000 days. A partial number of days is allowed; that is, you\n            can specify hours, minutes and so on, as a fraction of a day.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nbc1665702757240.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Packing Codes for Date and Time Data</a><p>Uniface data types Date, Time, and Datetime (and linear variations of these) are associated with a variety of packing codes.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531438\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531438\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Date and Time Data Types Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 26, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Date and Time Data Types Date and Time Data Types If a Date or Time field uses an E packing code, Uniface automatically adds a NULL date or time to the date to be stored. Datetime Data Type For a Datetime field, Uniface provides defaults in the case of partially filled fields: If both the date and time have been omitted, the value is assumed to be NULL. If the date has been omitted but a time is specified, the day, month and year default to the current day, the current month and the current year, respectively. If an incomplete date is specified, a missing day defaults to 1, a missing month defaults to the current month, and a missing year defaults to the current year. Linear Date and Time Data Types The range of values that a Linear Date field can have is from 0 (days) through 10,000 years (that is, 3,652,425 days). Only a whole number of days is allowed; that is, you cannot specify hours, minutes and ticks. The range of values that Linear Time may have is 0 to 24 hours. If more specific time information is required, use the Linear Datetime or Linear Date data type format. The range of values that a Linear Datetime field can have is from 0 days up to 10,000 days. A partial number of days is allowed; that is, you can specify hours, minutes and so on, as a fraction of a day. Related Links Packing Codes for Date and Time Data Uniface data types Date, Time, and Datetime (and linear variations of these) are associated with a variety of packing codes. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}